{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Meaning if the first one who will die is literally friends and relatives, that means I am automatically sentencing my family to death.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Interestingly enough, three weeks later, one of my co-prisoners, whom I knew very well, by the name of Slava, S-L-A-V-A capital L, Lederer, L-E-D-E-R-E-R, escaped with Beztek, successfully.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Into the camp walked one SS man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Out of the camp walked two SS men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He brought in a uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They boarded a train in Auschwitz and they went to Prague, with all the documents and everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And his escape was discovered seven hours later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was a general absolute panic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And interestingly enough, nothing happened, for it was arranged by an SS man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that was my [INAUDIBLE] escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now we'll go back to Schwarzheide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we are now at the gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the gate of Schwarzheide they are asking-- there are long tables.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are-- there is the SS, about six or eight SS men sitting there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are giving us new numbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got a new number, which we just had to sew on our striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I mercifully forgot the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It started with 60-- 65.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was 65,000 something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I forgot the whole number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were asking, simply, everybody should report his profession or his occupation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, if somebody was silly enough to put down that he's a doctor, for sure he ended with the latrine commander.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If he says that he's an engineer, so he would be carrying-- sorry, I have to specify.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were attached as a working commander to a factory, which had 65,000 civilian workers as were manufacturing gasoline, [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Synthing ?] gasoline out of coal.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
